  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink260-kilavi">pakaṟkuṟikkaṇ vanta talaimakaṉait tōḻi yiṉip puṉaṅkāvaṟku vārōm eṉakkūṟi varaivu kaṭāyatu. 
          </p>
        <p xml:lang="en">
          How the confidante urged marriage, saying, “We will no longer come to guard the field,” to the hero who came for the daytime tryst.
            
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink260">
<l>kuṉṟak kuṟavaṉ kātaṉ maṭamakaṇ</l>
<l>meṉṟōṭ koṭicciyaip peṟaṟkaritu tilla</l>
<l>paimpuṟap paṭukiḷi yōppalaḷ</l>
<l>puṉpula mayakkattu viḷaintaṉa tiṉaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>The beloved, naïve daughter of the hill dweller,</l>
        <l>she who is like a creeper, with tender shoulders,</l>
        <l>will be difficult to obtain.</l>
        <l rend="space">She no [longer] chases away</l>
        <l>the green backed parakeets</l>
        <l>that descend [upon the fields],</l>
        <l rend="space">as the millets have ripened</l>
        <l>in the mixture of meagre soils.</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
